git numbers. Digit sum 5 gives me 5 as a single digit, then 14, 23, 32, 41, and 50. Moving to digit sum 7, I have the single digit 7 and I'm working through the two-digit combinations.\n\nFor digit sum 11, there's no single digit option since the maximum is 9, but two-digit numbers work when the first digit ranges from 2 to 9, giving me 29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74, 83, and 92.\n\nMoving to digit sum 13, I need two digits where a+b=13 with a between 4 and 9, which gives me 49, 58, 67, 76, 85, and 94—that's 6 numbers.\n\nFor digit sum 17, only two-digit combinations work: 89 and 98, so just 2 numbers there.\n\nAdding everything up: 3 + 4 + 6 + 8 + 8 + 6 + 2 = 37 total numbers.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":11383,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":11383},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd071240-0b37-4e41-a9f0-3fb74d9ca8f2","uuid":"cdb80292-c7ff-4df3-9608-1e0ea75c5704"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_019JLcT7cQXLbLQUERfJMPNg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"37\n\n---\n\n**Простые суммы цифр в диапазоне [1, 18]:** 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17\n\n| Сумма цифр | Числа | Кол-во |\n|---|---|---|\n| 2 | 2, 11, 20 | 3 |\n| 3 | 3, 12, 21, 30 | 4 |\n| 5 | 5, 14, 23, 32, 41, 50 | 6 |\n| 7 | 7, 16, 25, 34, 43, 52, 61, 70 | 8 |\n| 11 | 29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74, 83, 92 | 8 |\n| 13 | 49, 58, 67, 76, 85, 94 | 6 |\n| 17 | 89, 98 | 2 |\n\n**Логика подсчёта:**\n\nДля однозначных (1–9) сумма цифр равна самому числу. Для двузначных (10–99) — сумма десятков и единиц, диапазон от 1 до 18. Число 100 имеет сумму цифр 1, не простое.\n\nДля двузначного числа с суммой цифр $s$: первая цифра $a \\in [1,9]$, вторая $b = s - a \\in [0,9]$. 